	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribit <persName type="auto_name">Franciscus Portus</persName> ex <placeName type="auto_name">Italia</placeName> haberi magnos a <placeName type="auto_name">Turca</placeName> apparatus fieri terraque marique, <placeName ref="l522" cert="high">Venetos</placeName> timere, parare ipsos quoque classem satis magnam, 80 scilicet triremes et quinque grandiores, quas vulgo galeas grossas vocant.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Ducem <placeName ref="l1098" cert="high">Florentiae</placeName> sibi timere a rege Hispaniarum, qui filium comitis Petiliani fecit emissarium in ipsum ducem; is comitis filius loca quaedam munita et portum prope <placeName type="auto_name">Senam</placeName> occupasse dicitur, unde incursionibus quotidianis agrum Senensem et <placeName type="auto_name">Florentinum</placeName> infestet.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">[a tergo] <placeName type="auto_name">Nova</placeName> pro d. Bullingero.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
